title: Caitlin Thielen and....Cordarrelle Patterson? #92Noon
description: Caitlin Thielen joins husband Adam to discuss the Thielen Foundation's passion behind helping the community during the pandemic, and then former Vikings WR Cordarrelle Patterson cold-calls the show!
